==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pseudo-heart
<hw>Pseu"do-heart`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Pseudo-</ets> + <ets>heart</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any contractile vessel of invertebrates which is not of the nature
of a real heart, especially one of those pertaining to the excretory
system.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pseudo-hyperthophic</ent>⟦br⟧
